data.title: Hey folks!! CHAMPIONS starring Woody Harrelson and directed by Bobby Farrelly is in theaters March 10th! I'm so honored to be in this...
data.meta_description: 5,854 likes, 117 comments - bubblestpb on March 1, 2023: "Hey folks!! CHAMPIONS starring Woody Harrelson and directed by Bobby Farrelly is in theaters March 10th! I'm so honored to be in this thing! Working with Woody and Bobby together was definitely another bucket list item for me. I was just at the premiere in New York City and it is truly great, the feel good movie of the year! The Friends rock! Check it out! @championsthefilm @woodyharrelson @kaitlinolson @cheechandchong @erniehudsonofficial".
